  <h1>Military Record</h1>
  <p class="page-meta">Sources: KOL.722/3, KOL.722/7, KOL.722/8, KOL.722/17 &middot; Polish Institute and Sikorski Museum, London; US Army Personal History Statements (DA Form 643A, DD Form 398, 1951&ndash;1954); Army of the United States Separation Qualification Record (WD AGO Form 100, 1946); Polish Government-in-Exile documents (Paris/London, 1940&ndash;1941); Wartime diary of Paul F. Sapieha, July 1944 &ndash; June 1945 (KOL.722/17)</p>

  <h2>Service Summary</h2>

